{"tid":1598040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開個ac就係為左幫個fd爆料","createTime":"2019-09-27T08:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T14:05:57.000Z","uid":319067,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b85aa774095acb83f353d7c5a6856a029557e3c5","tid":1598040,"uid":319067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"今日我忍5住要爆呢個仆街出黎<br />\n個死老野鐘華新其實就係有份搞到宜家個香港今，佢本來就有黑底，14號跟9江街肥狗，宜家走左去幫東江縱隊做野，香港咩拆國旗同烏蛟騰單野都係佢搵人做，目的大家都知就係為左抹黑啲示威者，再之後佢就出面掛翻啲國旗抺翻乾淨啲字，姐係光復香港個啲，個啲咩組隊唱國歌個啲不嬲佢都有份搵人搞，5講我諗真係無人知，佢不停做埋啲今既野就係為左係東江縱隊面前出位，因為中共每個月都出萬幾蚊人仔糧俾佢，中國海關仲係關口附近俾左間屋佢住，佢宜家就5住放租出去，住係香港元朗既馬田牌坊後面，姐係其實佢每個月係收緊幾雞野人仔糧，為錢出埋香港人，仲有佢細佬叫鐘華東，呢個又係仆街黎，恃住佢丫哥同大陸有啲關係就老千，呃中港牌錢，個牌仲可以過關行特別通道既大家知咩料，圖都有啦5好搵我老母btw就無吹水既，5信既人可以自己去fc下佢2條撚樣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係大佬鐘華新<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ieitvuQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FieitvuQ.jpg&h=47065a09&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vHvr1Bw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvHvr1Bw.jpg&h=1c649bc5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q3rCoPR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq3rCoPR.jpg&h=5a0bedbf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jugVUWx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjugVUWx.jpg&h=56f5578b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家呢個就係佢細佬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sxipOgL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsxipOgL.jpg&h=411fee27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fpF0mBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfpF0mBM.jpg&h=0a8426b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fifccJs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfifccJs.jpg&h=f52d39b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家千其5好玩人電話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src